node.text:
BLOATING AND “MORNING SKINNY”
 - I felt the need to make a post on this page about bloating and what is commonly known as being morning skinny etc, firstly I want to make it totally clear that bloating is totally normal and every single person in the world experiences it - the first photo is me in the morning having just woken up and the second is me just before going to bed at the end of the day - in modern society people often become obsessed with this idea that bloated isn’t an “attractive look” or that it isn’t normal when in actual fact it is. It is human and is our bodies way of remaining healthy and digesting food etc without bloating we wouldn’t be human nor healthy - 
Fitness and health isn’t about the way you look it’s about feeling healthy and happy and being proud of you and your body and loving yourself - it took me a long time to be truly happy with myself and my body shape but I can say I love me and my body now whether I look like the first photo or the second. I know that I do fitness for myself and to make myself happy - everyone is on a journey and a road that leads you different ways and at the end of the day we are all human and I cannot express it enough that BLOATING IS NORMAL AND YOU SHOULD LOVE YOURSELF AND YOUR BODY 😚 
Everyone is perfect in their own way and that’s what makes everyone unique and you who you are 😊 
Hope you guys all had a lovely Saturday - please feel free to DM me if you wanna chat or have any questions :)) xxx

#ko #selfmade #hundeboxen 

Was für ein langer Tag....
Morgens früh um halb 7 aus den Federn, schnell noch zum #baumarkt gefahren, vergessene Teile geholt.
Schnell heim, eine einhalb Stunden später schnell die Hunde versorgt, sowie auch uns.
Werkzeug-, Material, Hundechaos. Alles auf bauen, ca 10/10.30 haben wir los gelegt.
Nach einigen hin und her ist uns aufgefallen, dass wir einen Denkfehler hatten bei der Schienenmontage...alles wieder weg. Neu montiert, passt! 
Grundplatte war schon vom Bauhaus auf dem richtigen Maß, kleine Anpassungen haben wir an den Seitenteilen vorgenommen. Zu erst haben die Luana und Aika ihre Seite fertiggestellt. Die Seitenteile mit Innenwinkeln verstärkt.
Alle anderen Bretter gesägt, geschraubt, gebohrt, entgradet und festgeschraubt.
Nach einem Tag Arbeit, Hälfte geschafft 💪🏻🤪🤭
Morgen noch ein bisschen was wir im Haus machen können ohne viel Krach.

✨Gute Nachti🌙😌

——————————

shortcode_media.accessibility_caption: Photo by BH em Detalhes in Jequitibá with @jozanefaleiro, @memorial.vale, @folclorejequitiba, and @luz.comunica. Image may contain: sky and outdoor.

node.text: 👏👏 viva a valorização da cultura! Viva o folclore e as manifestações culturais!
👏👏 viva a valorização da cultura! Viva o folclore e as manifestações culturais!

A 32ª edição do Festival de Folclore de Jequitibá @folclorejequitiba está sendo apresentada pelo Memorial Vale em uma série de vídeos com cenas e relatos das festividades, publicados às 11h00, no YouTube, até o dia 30 de agosto.

Jequitibá é considerada a Capital Mineira do Folclore. Devido à pandemia, este ano a programação será virtual. Em parceria com o @memorial.vale, será possível mostrar a beleza das manifestações culturais dessa festa, como as apresentações de Congado, Folia de Reis, Folia do Divino, Pastorinhas, Fim de Capina, Encomendação das Almas, Fileira Sagrada e Dança do Tear, além dos musicais.

-----------------------------------
📆 De 22 a 30 de agosto.
🕰️ 11h00.
💻 Canal do YouTube do @memorial.vale.
📸 Nacip Gomez.
📄 @luz.comunica / @jozanefaleiro.

the past few months has been a roller coaster of emotions, more negative than positive. the constant anguish over the uncertain future and the jarring fact that i’ll be graduating during the worst recession in a century. although, home is  somewhere my heart lies but i don’t really enjoy being home as such. i always end up in stupid arguments, it makes me so frustrated and i don’t know where to take it out. however, i learned to focus my energy to heal instead of fueling my complex,,,
today, i look at things too carefully and i've been thinking about how everything around the corner has their hands tied to a moment that plays around them over and over again. i'm aware of the parts of myself which i’ve always neglected, and they mostly include the love i’ve for certain people in my life,,,, the world still moves like a blur but i forgive myself faster than it can revolve.
.

node.text:
“Todos os dias Deus nos dá – junto com o sol – um momento em que é possível mudar tudo que nos deixa infelizes. 
Todos os dias procuramos fingir que não percebemos este momento, que ele não existe, que hoje é igual a ontem e será igual a amanhã. 
Mas, quem presta atenção ao seu dia, descobre o instante mágico. Ele pode estar escondido na hora em que enfiamos a chave na porta pela manhã, no instante de silêncio logo após o jantar, nas mil e uma coisas que nos parecem iguais. 
Este momento existe – um momento em que toda a força das estrelas passa por nós, e nos permite fazer milagres. 
A felicidade às vezes é uma bênção – mas geralmente é uma conquista. 
O instante mágico do dia nos ajuda a mudar, nos faz ir em busca de nossos sonhos. 
Vamos enfrentar muitas desilusões – mas tudo é passageiro, e não deixa marcas. E, no futuro, podemos olhar para trás com orgulho e fé”.
.
Paulo Coelho
.

node.text:
.
人は自分を
受け入れる程度にしか
他人を受け入れることは
できません。

相手に多くを求めない。
相手を自由にすること。
それが関係を続けることです。

認める事ができない事を
認める事。
それで解決。

自分に正直になったとき
大方のことは解決します。

困難には正面から
向き合っていくこと。
問題から逃げると
問題は大きくなります。

しがみついているものから
ちょっと手を離すと
幸せになれます。

どうにもならなくなった時は
生きていること自体に価値がある
と信じること。

人に対して
自分の意見や気持ちを
伝えられるようになって
一人前の大人。

今が幸せなら
過去のことは全て許せます。

加藤諦三
私の心の先生。
.
.
.

Write and Wipe Activity Card✍🏻
اجعلي تعلم الرياضيات و الحروف أمرًا سهلاً وممتعًا لطفلك...
تحتوي هذه المجموعة على ٦٠ بطاقة قابلة لإعادة الاستخدام والكتابة والمسح.

✨✨✨✨✨

🟡 المجموعة الأولى لتعلم الأعداد والجمع والطرح وممارسة الكتابة...
- تحتوي على جميع الأرقام من ١ إلى ١٠ كتابةً ولفظاً ليتمكن الطفل من تتبع النقط ثم إتقان كتابتها على السطر.
- كل بطاقة للرقم تحتوي على صور ليتمكن الطفل من عدّها وكتابة الناتج.
- تحتوي على عمليات للجمع والطرح بطريقة ممتعة وغير تقليدية.

✨✨✨✨✨✨

🟡 المجموعة الثانية لتعلم الحروف وممارسة مهارات الكتابة..
- تحتوي على جميع الحروف الإنجليزية بمراحل كتابة الحرف بالشكل الصحيح ليتمكن الطفل من تتبع النقط ثم إتقان كتابتها على السطر.
- كل بطاقة للحرف تحتوي على صورة لكلمة الحرف.
- تحتوي على بطاقات اخري لل Phonetic Symbol Vowels, Time and Clock, Weeks and Months...
🟡
كل مجموعة تحتوي على:
- قلم ماركر قابل للمسح
- قلم رصاص، ممحاة، براية
- ممحاة من القماش
- كُتيّب لممارسة جميع المهارات

* العمر المناسب: ٣ سنوات ومافوق
* السعر: ٩٥ ريال
